You can also create the demo appquickstartguide, which is an example app that displays Mojito documentation, by running the following commands:

  • $ mojito create demo quickstartguide qsg
  • $ cd qsg
  • $ node app.js
  • In a browser, navigate to the URLlocalhost:8666.
